file_content.text: Go home, Jedi--or the White Maw will devour you.
The White Maw is finished on Hoth. Please don't force me to kill you.
There is no death for Gen'Dai. Your pathetic lightsaber only tickles.
Not to criticize, but maybe we should've taken the Imperials....
Tickles, huh? I hope he likes to laugh.
T7 = setting all weapons maximum power
I'm told you can't be killed. Must come in handy.
Burn us, slice us, shoot us... we always come back. Gen'Dai live forever. You die today.
If he's so indestructible, why's he wearing all that armor?
If Jedi dies // T7 = avenge Jedi
The White Maw hungers. Feed it this fool!
Hard to chew when you don't have teeth.
You came here to die with the Jedi? That can be arranged.
